function Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WAITINGPERIOD return Boolean type tpValue : .Boolean
var p : Boolean

function Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WAITINGPERIODINDAYS return Int4 type tpValue : .Int4
var p : Int4
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(1, 5, 'Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WAITINGPERIODINDAYS') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFDate) var Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance : tWFDate var Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance : tWFDate var Coverage_Effective_Date : tWFDate
if self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WAITINGPERIOD = True ;-------------Member Eligibility End Date At Issuance----------- Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance = self.Member__HireDate + self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WAITINGPERIODINDAYS ;-----------Initial Enrollment Coverage Effective Date Calculation if self.Coverage__Enrollment_Period__Current_Enrollment_Period = cInitialEnrollment if Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance > self.GBP__Effective_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance elseif Eligibility_End_Date_At_Issuance <= self.GBP__Effective_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = self.GBP__Effective_Date endIf if Coverage_Effective_Date < self.Member__Division__EffectiveDate Coverage_Effective_Date = self.Member__Division__EffectiveDate elseif Coverage_Effective_Date < self.Contract__Signature_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = self.Contract__Signature_Date endIf endIf ;----------Member Eligibility End Date After Issuance---------- if self.Coverage__Enrollment_Period__Current_Enrollment_Period = cOngoingEnrollment Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance = self.Member__HireDate + self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__WAITINGPERIODINDAYS if Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance > self.Contract__Signature_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance elseif Eligibility_End_Date_After_Issuance <= self.Contract__Signature_Date Coverage_Effective_Date = self.Contract__Signature_Date if Coverage_Effective_Date < self.Member__Division__EffectiveDate Coverage_Effective_Date = self.Member__Division__EffectiveDate endIf endIf endIf ; else Coverage_Effective_Date = self.Member__HireDate endIf Result = Coverage_Effective_Date endProc

var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(GroupSize, 0, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
procedure Set_Value__Coverage__Dynamic_Data__GIAMOUNT(value : Num8) self.SetDynDataValue('GIAMOUNT', @value) endProc
function Coverage__Dynamic_Data__GIAMOUNT return Num8 type tpValue : .Num8
var p : Num8
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(1, 5, 'Coverage__Dynamic_Data__GIAMOUNT') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc

var p : Num8

procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Boolean) var modifiedField : Int4
Result = True ; ; ; Set GI Amount ; self.Set_Value__Coverage__Dynamic_Data__GIAMOUNT(self.InitGuaranteeIssueBenefitAmount(self.GBP__Group_Size)) ; ; Group Underwriting if there is a value modified from default ; modifiedField = 0 ; GI Amount if (self.GBP__Group_Size >= 100) and (self.GBP__Group_Size <= 999) and (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__GIAMOUNT <> 20000) modifiedField++ endIf if (self.GBP__Group_Size >= 1000) and (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__GIAMOUNT <> 30000) modifiedField++ endIf ; Minimum hours per week < 16 if self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__MINWORKHOURSPERWEEK < 16 modifiedField++ endIf ; Faces amount minimum < 5000 or > 50000 if (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__MEMBERFACEAMTMIN < 5000) or (self.Coverage__Dynamic_Data__MEMBERFACEAMTMIN > 50000) modifiedField++ endIf ; if modifiedField > 0 self.Set_Value__Coverage__Dynamic_Data__ATTRIBUTETRIGGERSUW(True) endIf endProc
